I have dry, distant times from the Lord, too. <br>
Without Him, life seems to filter through my eye and my thoughts with a lot of baggage and darkness and emptiness.<br>
It's especially then, that I know I need to stop.<br>
Stop and clear away a day or even a few hours to spend in solid worship and prayer. Take a day to myself and commit to spend it in communion with Him, and Him alone. It makes a world of difference, literally.<br>
So, I encourage you. Take a day, rest in His holiness. Find yourself in Him. Rid the distractions of this life and be still before Him.<br>
<br>
I've just learned recently, that I NEED to spend every morning listening to my worship music and reading my Bible ...in order to start my day off right, in order that my life, my day might be filtered through His thoughts, His truths and not my own.<br>
<br>
God always has something fresh and new for us to learn and grasp and exercise every morning. I love that about Him. That's why it never gets old or tiresome...because His thoughts are not ours, His ways are not ours. <br>
<br>
It's a constant challenge, to practice His ways and not MY ways. <br>
<br>
I'll be praying for you, that you are able to clear aways the stuff of life each day so that you may spend it in rest and renewal with Him.<br>
<br>
He sees you...as no one else truly does. He'll meet with you.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.showPrevMessage?topicID=24.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.showNextMessage?topicID=24.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=24.topic&index=12><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.emailToFriend?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.threadControl?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm27.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum met